info.name: German Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multiple layers of German dark chocolate sponge topped with light chocolate cream, vanilla cream and infused with dark and sour cherry compote. it is finished with a cherry and choco curls. The darker and more sour cherries make it an authentic german black forest cake recipe.

info.name: Red Velvet Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A rich molten vanilla cake with a buttermilk sponge and cream cheese, topped with whipped cream and dusted with red velvet crumbs. There are no artificial colours. The red velvet uses beetroot for colour. This is the original Red Velvet recipe that started in the United States.

info.name: Chocolate Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A thick layered velvety chocolate classic in a jar

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfct construction of red velvet goodness, carfully layered with vanilla cream and infused with vanilla essence makes for the perfect red velvet cake in a jar

info.name: Blueberry Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | An exotic mix of fresh blueberry pulp and freshly baked cake in a jar is a seasoal treat

info.name: Blueberry Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A light & creamy cheese cake with blueberry pulp baked with cream cheese

info.name: Blueberry Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Fresh blueberry pulp topped with whipped cream & sprinkles in a cup cake

info.name: Vanilla Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic cupcake with vanilla whippd cream adn edible sugar sprinkles

info.name: Classic Walnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic brownie Bakingo style. Infused with milkmaid, fresh cream and Vanleer dark chocolate, inundated with walnuts.

info.name: Nutella Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | The quintessential indulgent brownie prepared with milk maid, fresh cream & CHD 45 Chocolate, infused with Nutella and hazelnuts.

info.name: Trio Mousse Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A decadent trio of white chocolate, milk chocolate, CHD 45 chocolate & egg topped off with a rich cream.

info.name: Nutella Hazelnut Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is layered with chocolate hazelnut mousee, dark chocolate, milk chocolate fresh cream and molten nutella.

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Cake (600 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is blended with dark chocolate mousse and a crunchy French biscuit. The cake is topped off with a light chocolate drop and a chocolate garnish. A recipe that originated in Europe.

info.name: Ferrero Rocher Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A Ferrero Rocher cake is a delightful and indulgent dessert that incorporates the popular Ferrero Rocher chocolates into a cake

info.name: Dream Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | It's a luscious chocolate cake with layers of rich chocolate ganache, making it a decadent treat.

info.name: Tiramisu Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A sponge cake soaked in expresso coffee, layered with mascarpone cheese, topped with freshly whipped cream and dusted with cocoa. Bakingo’s rendition of a classic Italian Tiramisu recipe.
